
Overview of noun mafia

The noun mafia has 3 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                        
1. Mafia, Maffia, Cosa Nostra -- (a crime syndicate in the United States; organized in families; believed to have important relations to the Sicilian Mafia)
2. Mafia, Maffia, Sicilian Mafia -- (a secret terrorist group in Sicily; originally opposed tyranny but evolved into a criminal organization in the middle of the 19th century)
3. mafia, maffia -- (any tightly knit group of trusted associates)
